{"tid":1418213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正確應對途人影相嘅方法","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T11:27:53.000Z","uid":39752,"like":98,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4306c3b4eee04ada9c3233cad018d2481f478b05","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"不要說<br />\n唔好影相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影撚完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試著說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該要影相影背面吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無反應可能係唔知你叫緊佢<br />\n就拍佢膊頭再講同一句<br />\n<br />\n咁樣唔會令八卦路人反感<br />\n同時會識別到惡意藍絲<br />\n<br />\n通常你一講影背面<br />\n途人會即刻明白，亦唔會覺得你兇佢<br />\n有一半人會放棄唔影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果咁樣講完都唔聽唔應<br />\n特別係影大頭嘅人<br />\n咁就九成九有鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n遇到鬼嘅時候<br />\n第一件事唔係追屌<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>靜靜退後影返佢大頭同埋個芒</strong></span></span><br />\n跟住先開始處理藍絲程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多唔使好大動作就開到相機+影嘅捷徑<br />\n大家自己研究一下費事教精三毛用相同方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474f360f99ef052e03895112d82ec27259bea4ad","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b6efbe886e8e0a373d94dff304262540189213","tid":1418213,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:08:25.000Z","msg":"珍, 一開始好聲好氣 唔好影大頭就解決到, 佢繼續就影低罪證"},{"pid":"dd4830087452e58e1c73c4080caec5feb71b7b4b","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:10:41.000Z","msg":"你唔會知道個三姑六婆係咪影相上 whatsapp 話「啲後生仔都好和平吖」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e4de35d729dc6294b9a529305c74005bc11dbf","tid":1418213,"uid":199911,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"禮貌同客氣小小 接受程度就高好多"},{"pid":"a00915eac786efbbbe7615df714086224071c50c","tid":1418213,"uid":179875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:16:38.000Z","msg":"北角龍頭係碼眼見有幾個街坊屌番轉頭「影相又點撚樣」<br />\n<br />\n有人支持 有人反對 有人鐘意你地 自然有人唔鐘意<br />\n<br />\n咁好啦, 如果d街坊/遊客係都要影, 眼見既都係花生友遠距離影, 唔delete, 企硬同你地嘈. 你地打算點? 打撚7佢地? <br />\n<br />\n呢點今日我眼見覺得好有問題, 得罪支持你地既人係遲早問題"},{"pid":"530a1ec1c6d2a21b5b88599783d63a41d0a5f685","tid":1418213,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4306c3b4eee04ada9c3233cad018d2481f478b05","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"不要說<br />\n唔好影相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影撚完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試著說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該要影相影背面吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無反應可能係唔知你叫緊佢<br />\n就拍佢膊頭再講同一句<br />\n<br />\n咁樣唔會令八卦路人反感<br />\n同時會識別到惡意藍絲<br />\n<br />\n通常你一講影背面<br />\n途人會即刻明白，亦唔會覺得你兇佢<br />\n有一半人會放棄唔影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果咁樣講完都唔聽唔應<br />\n特別係影大頭嘅人<br />\n咁就九成九有鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n遇到鬼嘅時候<br />\n第一件事唔係追屌<br />\n而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>靜靜退後影返佢大頭同埋個芒</strong></span></span><br />\n跟住先開始處理藍絲程序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有好多唔使好大動作就開到相機+影嘅捷徑<br />\n大家自己研究一下費事教精三毛用相同方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"現場好多人影相,大家都係為左打卡,值唔值得為左一張相換人地青春先?請正視,前線已經好多野做,唔好增加人地負擔啦"},{"pid":"9bc5b3d62912215c6ec6b768ada9310dc6c9ed5c","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"點解要講<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>影背面吖</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n而唔係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該唔好影相</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好影大頭呀</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n因為前者係一種符合佢利益嘅建議<br />\n到最後佢如果唔影，係佢自己發現唔好<br />\n<br />\n而後者不符合佢利益，直接就有反抗心理<br />\n覺得係<strong>你令佢無得影</strong><br />\n而「唔好影大頭」，咁乜嘢係「好」呢？<br />\n影相嘅人唔覺自己錯但覺得莫名其妙俾人屌咗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直接話俾人聽「應該點做」<br />\n相比起講「唔好點做」更加入腦易跟隨</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d6ee757515ba91ed6cfbd622889ddf465380ddbf","tid":1418213,"uid":96708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/teZ1tYU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FteZ1tYU.png&h=cb01e009&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d191c7d12e8bad3296347096e550b01ce64333e9","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530a1ec1c6d2a21b5b88599783d63a41d0a5f685","tid":1418213,"uid":4746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4306c3b4eee04ada9c3233cad018d2481f478b05","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"不要說<br />\n唔好影相呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影撚完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n試著說<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔該要影相影背面吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n無反應可能係唔知你叫緊佢<br />\n就拍佢膊頭再講同一句