","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dede2c764916bd750356582859dd698db19cfc6e","tid":1418213,"uid":277873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:18:00.000Z","msg":"尋日係一個遠到根本影唔到前線既位置，只係得啲疏散緊既人流，人流中有黑衫有街坊（好多係唔知乜事被人話危險叫行返轉頭），無人有gear其實無嘢好影。<br />\n突然間就出現咗呢種衝突<br />\n幾個人圍咗個阿伯凶佢話佢影乜<br />\n<br />\n其實我真係覺得無必要咁惡<br />\n佢好可能真係八卦想影吓奇觀既街坊<br />\n<br />\n然後我睇住好幾個根本唔知乜事（連前面有突發示威都未知）既師奶，好驚咁遠遠望住凶人果幾個黑衫&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n何必呢"},{"pid":"b53def7202ef4880cc26417d5a6b888d59388731","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a59f64f852b68ab6decb0be7f0255a5bd1cd7d","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:53:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2dcd461af29c78307a09ff2036bd6f4c45f41f7","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:19:38.000Z","msg":"咪睇狗吠啦幫手推兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc8fd06e36b6ee1957500264f90d584f4b6d7f4","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"我會自己十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4cd3e525dfd1129c0d31695118dcb8226e7a65","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T08:53:14.000Z","msg":"我現時自己肯十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c332f6ca3221e989ab165432dea2474165c3dea5","tid":1418213,"uid":39752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"唔記得數到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=